&lt;p&gt;***Please note this is an INTERNAL VACANCY ONLY for NUH employees, therefore only current employees of Nottingham University Hospitals NHS Trust will be considered for the post.***&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CAS division are looking for a motivated and forward thinking PA for the CAS matron team. This role would entail working 2.5 days per week support the matron team. Tasks will include diary management , appointment booking , telephone answering , typing up of letters, note taking , filing and any other administrative duties required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The days required are Thursday, Friday and a half day on Wednesday but flexibility would be desirable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates must have extensive experience using NUH Computer systems such as Medway , Nervecentre, healthroster, TRAC, safer staffing and Notis plus be able to compile excel spread sheets&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name-Alison Dalton&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title-Deputy Divisional nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address-alison.dalton@nuh.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number-07812 268038&lt;/p&gt;
